Steps
1. Ctrl+Click fold icon (E3) on fully expanded node (S1)
2. Verify entire subtree enters recursively folded state (S4), all descendants hidden
3. Click unfold icon (E2) on recursively folded node (S4)
4. Verify node returns to fully expanded state (S1), all descendants visible
